e was wearing was assumed lost, but had apparently stayed in the eyelid for 28 years."SOURCES: CNN, BMJ Case Reportshttps://edition.cnn.com/2018/08/15/health/contact-lens-eyelid-study/index.htmlhttp://casereports.bmj.com/content/2018/bcr-2018-225767.fullv***]]></description>
